  "title": "Retail Associate | Mass Hiring | Islandwide - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Position Title: Retail Associate</strong></u></p><ul><li>Working Days: Hours: 44hrs / week</li><li>Location: Islandwide</li></ul><p><u>Key Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Assist customers with product queries, recommendations, and purchases.</li><li>Handle cashiering duties including payments, refunds, and closing of daily sales.</li><li>Replenish stocks, maintain proper product display, and ensure store cleanliness.</li><li>Perform inventory checks and assist in stock-taking activities.</li><li>Ensure promotional materials and price tags are updated.</li><li>Handle customer feedback or escalate issues when necessary.</li><li>Support store opening and closing procedures.</li></ul><p><u>Requirements:</u></p><ul><li>Preferably with prior retail or customer service experience</li><li>Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays as required.</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
